SIMPLE: untraded
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untraded
<hw>Un*trad"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
dealt with in trade; not visited for purposes of trade.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Hakluyt</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unpracticed; inexperienced.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Udall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not traded in or bartered; hence, not hackneyed;
unusual; not common.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untrained</ent>⟦br⟧
